snippet.title: Best VGM 785 - The Magical Quest starring Mickey Mouse - Dark Forest
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
The Magical Quest starring Mickey Mouse (1992)
Dark Forest
Mari Yamaguchi
